data.description: Don't pass this one up! Great location & floorplan! Freshly painted in the last year & the carpet has been pulled up to expose the beautiful hardwood floors. This roomy 3 bedroom, 2 bath ranch won't disappoint! Adorable eat in kitchen opens to both a living room & a family room. Beautiful stone fireplace & window seat with storage completes the large family room. Spacious enough for a large dining room table. Step out to the patio & fenced in area that houses a new Intex pool that will stay. It's  9 x 18 & 4 1/2 ft deep. There are 2 raised garden beds that produced tons of veggies this year. The large garage faces the alley & has a window unit that stays and a ceiling fan. Doubles as a great workshop. Restaurants, shopping & grade school are nearby.
